snippet.title: Starkeepers - Official World Premiere Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2022
snippet.description:
Build a new world together in epic fantasy Starkeepers, coming to Steam Early Access in 2023. In this exclusive world premiere gameplay trailer, see how indie developer Wolfpack is shaping this experimental community-driven MMORPG. Wolfpack includes team members with experience on the development teams of Warframe, Age of Conan, and more.

#IGN #Gaming #IGNSummerOfGaming
